===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The junction of two (or more) paths, [[street]]s, highways, or other thoroughfares.
# {{geometry}} The point or set of points common to two geometrical objects (such as the point where two lines meet or the line where two planes intersect).
# {{settheory}} The [[set]] containing all the [[element]]s that are common to two or more sets.

